data.description: MLS# 269463 What a gem! Walk through the front door to see the BREATHTAKING views of the Snake River. This Charbonneau Park home is beautifully updated and offers 3 beds, 2 baths with a split bedroom layout. Chefs will love the newly updated kitchen with quartz counters, beautiful wood cabinets, soft close drawers, ample storage, lots of counter space, and newer stainless appliances that all stay. This home is move in ready on nearly a 1/2 acre of low maintenance grounds. Take in the seasons and views off the large deck that is perfect for entertaining or relaxing with a book. You are within walking distance of water activities, boat launch, and campgrounds at the popular Charbonneau Park. Enjoy this home year round or create income as an Airbnb. Features: Roof (approximately 4 years old), HVAC (1.5 years old), new flooring, new siding & exterior paint, newer W/D that stay, new vinyl windows, newer kitchen SS appliances that stay. Come see this gem before it is gone!
